List of levels

poison/lightning aoe - use trolls tanking
fire - flame imp triggers vents to keep goblins safe
trapdoor - 3 reusable trapdoors, timing puzzle with goblins
bat intro - learn that bats can fly up open trapdoors
reuse trapdoor - time the trigger to get one across
lightning - cage goblin to protect flame imp
ArrowsAndDoors - Spider + goblins protected by ogre and shaman
